oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Hank Snow Benefit at the Grand Ole Opry - Year 5 - Part 3
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The recording is of the Hank Snow Benefit Concert at the Grand Ole Opry. The segment is hosted by T. Tommy Cutrer (musician) and features performances by: Hank Williams Jr. (musician) and Willie Nelson (musician). The recording is from an unidentified date. The tape is identified as the fifth year of the program. The tape is part three of three.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Hank Williams Jr.; T. Tommy Cutrer; Willie Nelson; Bobbie Nelson
